            "text": "業務内容の範囲"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760819075125-or1jsok3d",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-zqw75slrv-6363e627-65c1-4f6c-a7cd-20a8eabdeb0c",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "さらに詳しく：看護助手と准看護師の業務内容の違い"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760819075125-w8zjdqugv",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-go52j1b22",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手は、医療行為は行えませんが、患者さんの生活を支える上で欠かせない存在です。具体的には、以下のような業務を行います。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760819075125-2tkrdt6im",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-0j4nfrbq7-387e0c12-366c-4883-a798-a22ee07e24bb",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-0j4nfrbq7-b11bbe67-0558-4a44-a0b1-dccd8051e426",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "環境整備:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-0j4nfrbq7-a9d94bc9-c958-4834-ae0f-0c5054b8e08a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 病室の清掃、ベッドメイキング、物品の整理整頓など、患者さんが快適に過ごせる環境を整えます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760819075125-gy6g7bboi",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-2m979behf-8b9de79d-fce1-4583-b31c-73cfc55640a2",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-2m979behf-d73d46a5-0d19-47d6-8a6f-f14ec252b12e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "患者さんの介助:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760819075125-2m979behf-ef361d66-0d3c-4820-a4f5-9afcf51ecce2",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 食事、入浴、排泄、着替えなどの介助を行います。患者さんの状態に合わせて、安全に、そして尊厳を保てるように配慮することが重要です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
