        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block--8446521892015027344",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-373389077394698207",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "まとめ"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-eb1cc51e-6351-442c-9d32-c7aaef20ba11",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-62a408f4-3bea-4065-978f-aef81a285119",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手と准看護師の違いとは？でお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-d042d547-bae2-49ca-b572-8ff5575ed68a",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-b8886269-7ce7-44d9-8b57-abd3ec9d36bd",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-abe1886f-d4c8-4567-afbe-9e3aedae9f42",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-a27dd51f-ab6c-4807-b8b9-53c2511000e0",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手と准看護師の基本的な違いの視点で資格の有無に目を向ける"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-263cecb5-54c1-44d4-85ab-faaa38631eb3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-9c8676f3-b525-47c2-851d-00067dad63f0",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手：特別な資格は不要です。未経験からでも働くことが可能です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-c8ca0a43-e880-4c03-8d41-b7846744a44d",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-a640833e-ea67-4405-b1d7-f393c748f392",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "准看護師：都道府県知事から発行される「准看護師免許」が必要です。養成学校で2年間学ぶ必要があります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-8abefce8-239d-49d6-b9d2-c440400a0a7a",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-c092d0cd-d8c9-4eb4-a73b-e8b63cf32ccf",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "あわてず一歩ずつ、チームと情報を共有しながら進めれば大丈夫です。今日の学びを小さく実践し、次の勤務につなげていきましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
